/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c68a832bf96093b0d27493f0034335073e27f149","tid":111724,"uid":29081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T15:37:28.000Z","msg":"係咪都係10.2.1?<br />\n今日我都試過一次得番4粒physical 鍵用到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa9508890a8a944a6658a4a77df4ef73d40c327e","tid":111724,"uid":83012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T15:39:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪都係10.2.1?<br />\n今日我都試過一次得番4粒physical 鍵用到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n10.2.1真係多暗病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6ce2cff06f824f280d07583b85874980247500a","tid":111724,"uid":47940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T15:40:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪都係10.2.1?<br />\n今日我都試過一次得番4粒physical 鍵用到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係呀<br />\n但未更新前都已經係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n開頭我都以為係自己未更新去10.2.1"},{"pid":"bf5ab120a2fd82cc6136fcc929886625e67bc089","tid":111724,"uid":57945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T15:40:33.000Z","msg":"應該係ios問題，下次試下擺佢係度幾分鐘再試下強制reboot"},{"pid":"aa807e6145cd496a40b34af340953bddfaec5cb0","tid":111724,"uid":61947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T15:48:02.000Z","msg":"如果部機唔多野嘅入DUF Mode 清部機一次。<br />\n<br />\n或，<br />\n<br />\n等下一個版本升上去再試下。<br />\n<br />\n再唔得，<br />\n<br />\n就應該係touch IC 有問題了。"},{"pid":"adb26fa12024440e0d3052d3a50d4b379974dfc9","tid":111724,"uid":47940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T15:51:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>應該係ios問題，下次試下擺佢係度幾分鐘再試下強制reboot</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 幾乎每日都要經歷強制reboot <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5241a4d6e1f7e0d5bbc2e4ccf0fa179812cfd38","tid":111724,"uid":47940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T15:52:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果部機唔多野嘅入DUF Mode 清部機一次。<br />\n<br />\n或，<br />\n<br />\n等下一個版本升上去再試下。<br />\n<br />\n再唔得，<br />\n<br />\n就應該係touch IC 有問題了。</blockquote><br />\n今日試佐duf mode 了<br />\n一個鐘後又黎料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6975130c3f16ff2869dd06d28058b4923d40a166","tid":111724,"uid":83012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T15:52:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果部機唔多野嘅入DUF Mode 清部機一次。<br />\n<br />\n或，<br />\n<br />\n等下一個版本升上去再試下。<br />\n<br />\n再唔得，<br />\n<br />\n就應該係touch IC 有問題了。</blockquote><br />\n比著我，我會等10.3正式版出先DFU升上10.3<br />\n之前由10.0.2升10.2.1已經唔對路"},{"pid":"09e5af49e3e8e22385b3db2496e41f7108c02582","tid":111724,"uid":771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T15:59:47.000Z","msg":"部機屈得多，個touch 硬件就死，趁仲有反應攞去trade/賣"},{"pid":"e47e3dad94d1af347e8ab30f09b08afefa834a47","tid":111724,"uid":61947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T06:37:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>如果部機唔多野嘅入DUF Mode 清部機一次。<br />\n<br />\n或，<br />\n<br />\n等下一個版本升上去再試下。<br />\n<br />\n再唔得，<br />\n<br />\n就應該係touch IC 有問題了。</blockquote><br />\n今日試佐duf mode 了<br />\n一個鐘後又黎料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n試下DUF mode 裝iOS 10.3 beta ，如果再係咁，就拎去天才吧放低部機check check 啦。<br />\n<br />\n部機個mon touch 唔到時拎去天才吧，去得天才吧就換翻新機，touch IC 工程都幾大下，應該唔幫妳換架啦。"},{"pid":"2676b05e22a95747d43eae7eae5c0f200c57c5b7","tid":111724,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T08:17:32.000Z","msg":"X2"}]}